  "summary": "Calculate the NPV of a project by discounting expected cash flows at the appropriate discount rate.",
  "prompt": "A firm has an expected cash flow of $150,000 in Year 1, $200,000 in Year 2, and $250,000 in Year 3. If the appropriate discount rate is 8%, calculate the NPV of the project.",
  "options": [],
  "correct_option": "526931.64",
